{
  "stem": "16473.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And mother asked all those women if they would take me into their bed and none of them would, for reasons that they already saw, that if they called attention to themselves, probably they will be the next ones.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So mother told me to go under the covers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm trying to picture what covers was I under, because he was in her bed, where was I.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But all I know is I was under the covers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I kept saying, mother, mother, what is he doing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she'd say, and for years I thought she said, he's talking German to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what she said to me when we compared notes later was, he thinks I'm his bride.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So all that time-- this is another closing your eyes to things-- all that time I was under the covers, I did not want to know what was happening.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was another evidence of women's inhumanity to women, that you know somebody could have taken me in their bed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And mother was very upset about that subsequently.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But after that, I don't know when I'd mention this to you, maybe with the pictures, we kept mother from being discovered because every time the Russians came we'd know, they'd be knocking on the door, all kinds of noises.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mother would go under the covers, I'd get on top with my feet spread out, her head between my feet.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one time, we just distracted a Russian soldier that came and saw the cat-- oh, Russian, a cat, whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they went off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the point was that never again was mother going to be found in a position where this could happen to her again.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I each time was the intermediary, so I was frightened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was frightened.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
